“Ng’at morwakou, to orwako mana an, kendo ng’at morwaka to orwako mana Jal mane oora. 
41  Ka ng’ato orwako janabi nikech janabino en jaote Nyasaye, to noyud pok ma janabi yudo, kendo ng’at morwako ng’at makare nikech en ng’at makare, noyud pok ma ng’at makare yudo. 
42  Adier awachonu ni, ng’at momiyo japuonjrena moro matinie moloyo kata mana pi mang’ich omodho nikech ng’atno en japuonjrena, noyud pokne maonge kiawa.”

